These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
7 different games are played: bridge, chess, whist, scrabble, mah-jongg, billiard, backgammon
House: colonial, victorian, gothic-revival, tower, palace, cape-cod, ranch-style
 1. the ranch-style house is the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the colonial house is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
 3. the colonial house is not to the left of the victorian house##8
 4. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
 5. the person playing bridge is not to the left of the cape-cod house##8
 6. the person playing bridge is not the victorian house##6
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the person playing backgammon##8
 9. the palace house is somewhere between the ranch-style house and the victorian house##7
10. the victorian house is the person playing billiard##1
11. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
12. the cape-cod house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
13. the colonial house is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
14. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the palace house and the colonial house##7
15. the person playing billiard is on the left of the colonial house##1
16. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##8
17. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
18. the person playing backgammon is the gothic-revival house##1
19. the palace house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
20. the person playing scrabble is not the cape-cod house##6
21. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person playing bridge##8
22. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Game           | billiard | whist | backgammon | chess  | mah-jongg  | scrabble | bridge    |
| House   | victorian   | colonial   | gothic-revival   | tower | palace | ranch-style        | cape-cod |

