 1. the japanese is in the middle##1
 2. the spanish is not the person watching scientific movies##6
 3. the colombian is not to the left of the indian##8
 4. the spanish is between the indian and the person watching scientific movies##2
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the egyptian##1
 7. the person watching musical movies is in an odd position##4
 8. the colombian is not to the left of the egyptian##8
 9. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
10. the egyptian is on the left of the colombian##1
11. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
12. the french is not to the right of the egyptian##8
13. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8
14. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
15. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
16. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |      6      |      7      |
