 1. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the left of the person eating pear##8
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 4. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 6. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5
 8. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the left of the person eating pear##5
11. the person eating carrot is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who's hobby is camping##2
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is not the person eating avocado##6
14. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4     |      5       |      6      |    7    |
